


存款  save        account + =500
取款  withdraw    account - =500
转账  acc1 -=500,acc2 +=500
账单

交易主函数:(账户ID,交易类型，金额数量，其他参数)
make_transaction(account_idm,tran_type,amount,**kwargs)
    acc_data =get_acc_data(account_id)
    if tran_type == save
        acc_data[balance] += amount
    if tran_type == whitdraw
        acc_data[balance] -= amount
        acc_data[balance] -= amount *0.05
    if tran_type =="transfer"
        acc1[account] -=500
        acc2[account] +=500


account     账户 账单
tran_type   交易类型
    save        存款
    withdraw    取款
    transfer    转账
amount      金额 数量
balance     余额


